SPONSORSHIP & PARTNERSHIP

PARTNER WITH RIYADH FASHION WEEK

Riyadh Fashion Week offers exceptional opportunities for brands and organizations to align with one of the most prestigious fashion events in the Middle East. Our partnership programs are designed to create meaningful connections and deliver measurable value to our partners.

PARTNERSHIP PACKAGES

We offer various partnership levels designed to meet different objectives and budgets. From exclusive title sponsorships to category partnerships, we work closely with each partner to create customized programs that align with their brand goals.

PARTNERSHIP PROSPECTUS COMING SOON

PARTNERSHIP BENEFITS

  • Exclusive brand visibility across all event touchpoints
  • Direct access to fashion industry leaders and influencers
  • Customized marketing and promotional opportunities
  • VIP access to runway shows and exclusive events
  • Digital and social media amplification
  • Networking opportunities with international fashion professionals

INTERESTED IN PARTNERING?
